# Directories Bazel must not walk during package enumeration.
#
# This file protects the loading phase of `bazel build //...` and
# `bazel query //...` from foot-guns where workspace-local state
# directories either contain BUILD files (Bazel's own .cache execroot,
# nested repo clones) or contain large symlink trees.
.cache
.git
%workspace%
node_modules
out
